654
00:39:55,329 --> 00:39:57,599
Aku meneleponmu karena...

655
00:39:58,569 --> 00:39:59,599
Ya?

656
00:40:01,069 --> 00:40:03,240
Kudengar para pegawai telah pindah ke perusahaan lain

657
00:40:03,240 --> 00:40:06,410
